{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":7,"isBulletin":117},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6},"Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento","Caminneci, Parello, Soraci","2023","\u003Cspan>Valentina Caminneci, Maria Concetta Parello, e Cristina Soraci, «Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento», in \u003Ci>Indagini archeologiche nell’insula IV del Quartiere Ellenistico Romano di Agrigento, 2014-2018\u003C/i>, a c. di Valentina Caminneci et al. (L’Aquila: One Group Edizioni, 2023), 537–49\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/A7HRWIUH",[8],{"file":9,"uri":9,"title":10,"status":11,"editionAuthor":13,"type":14,"objectType":18,"material":22,"condition":29,"layoutDesc":30,"handNote":37,"date":51,"places":56,"geo":66,"country":61,"provenance":58,"provenanceGeo":70,"region":73,"settlement":63,"repository":74,"idno":78,"textLang":80,"tmNumber":29,"facsimile":84,"letterHeights":90,"publications":95,"zotero":97,"keywords":99,"html":109,"bibl":110,"bulletinDateSort":116,"citedRangeSort":111,"languageSort":81,"materialSort":23,"typeSort":15},"ISic001830","Building inscription of Martinianos",{"_":12},"draft",null,{"_":15,"ana":16,"ref":17},"building","#function.building","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},"plaque","#object.plaque","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259",{"_":23,"ana":24,"type":25,"subtype":26,"ref":28},"marble","#material.inorganic.stone","stone.unspecified",[27],"unverified","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html","",{"layout":31},{"p":32,"rs":33,"damage":29},"Traces of three lines of ancient Greek are preserved, with guidelines above and below; upper, left and right margins are partially preserved. The text appears to maintain a consistent margin on the left, but not on the right.",{"_":34,"ana":35,"ref":36},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":38,"dimensions":39},"Tall, regular, narrow letters, v-cut, with small serifs on the termination of strokes. Small deep triangular interpuncts. Alpha has broken bar; epsilon tall, narrow, with equal short horizontals; theta and omicron are rhomboid; mu has vertical first and last, with the diagonals starting below the top and only desencing to the mid-point; nu is similar; rho has small curved, closed loop; sigma is lunate but rectilinear, with very short horizontals.",[40,47],{"type":41,"l":42,"from":43,"to":44,"h":45,"unit":46,"atLeast":45,"atMost":45},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","110","mm",{"type":48,"l":49,"from":43,"to":44,"h":50,"unit":46,"atLeast":50,"atMost":50},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","20",{"_":52,"notBefore":53,"notAfter":54,"evidence":55},"Dated by reference to Flavius Martinianos, consularis of Sicily between 352 and 358 CE (Soraci)",352,358,"prosopography",[57,62],{"_":58,"type":59,"ref":60,"region":61},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086","Sicilia",{"_":63,"type":64,"ref":65,"region":61},"Agrigento","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[67],[68,69],37.32084,13.58876,[71,72],37.297649,13.591579,"Sicily",{"_":75,"role":76,"ref":77},"Parco Archeologico Valle dei Templi","site","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/200",{"type":79},"inventory",{"_":81,"mainLang":82,"languages":83},"Ancient Greek","grc",[81],{"n":85,"url":86,"height":87,"width":88,"desc":29,"surfaceType":89},"screen","ISic001830_tiled.tif","5520px","3680px","front",[91,93],{"atLeast":92,"atMost":92},110,{"atLeast":94,"atMost":94},20,[96],"Caminneci, Parello, Soraci, 2023, Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",[98],"A7HRWIUH",[100,101,102,15,19,23,103,104,105,106,104,107,108,82],"isic001830","building inscription of martinianos",{"_":12},"agrigentum","agrigento","sicilia","sicily","parco archeologico valle dei templi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv 